title: Artist Set of 20 Wash-out Markers
description:
This cool stationery set makes the perfect gift for creative kids who love to color and draw. Set contains 20 double-ended fabric markers with both broad and fine tips in every color you can imagine and comes in a fun, handy tube. These versatile pens work great on machine-washable textiles and even on paper and stationery, too!
  • Dimensions: 7.3 x 2.6 in.
  • Materials: Plastic/cardboard tube
